               <msContents>
                  <summary>Harp of Praise, <foreign xml:lang="gez">አርጋኖነ፡ ውዳሴ</foreign>; Two Miracles of Mary, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተአምረ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign></summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="146r" facs="003">Fols 1r–146r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1344enzira">ʿƎnzirā
                                                  sǝbḥat</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                       በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሥሉስ፡ ዘእንበበለ፡ (sic) ፍልጠት፡ ወአሐዱ፡ በጽምረት፡ ኅቡረ፡ ህላዌ፡ ዕሩየ፡ መለኮት፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ንጽሕፍ፡ እንከ፡ ዘንተ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ዘይሰመይ፡ አርጋኖነ፡ ውዳሴ፡ ወመሰንቆ፡ መዝሙር፡ ወእንዚራ፡ ስብሐት፡ ዘአስተብፅዖ፡ ድንግልናሃ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>

